            "code" : "900000000000550004",
            "display" : "Definition (core metadata concept)"
          },
          "value" : "A hypothesis testing measure that is the probability that a statistic value derived from a posterior predictive distribution under the assumptions of the model is equal to or more extreme than the observed posterior value of the statistic."
